    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Glow Plug Sleeve Installation</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Be certain that the glow plug recess was cleaned out with a Glow Plug Sleeve Seat Wire Brush ,
                    rinsed with a suitable cleaning solution, and blown out with shop air.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <figure id="f2650474" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd08/D0862.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 170. Application of liquid gasket to sleeve</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Wall (end)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Upper wall (top)</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Liquid Gasket (RTV) to the two locations on the glow plug sleeve.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2350463" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd08/D0863.webp" type="gif" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 171. Installing glow plug sleeve</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Glow Plug Sleeve Installer</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Glow plug sleeve</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install glow plug sleeve into cylinder head with the Glow Plug Sleeve Installer .</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2350464" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd08/D0864.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 172. Installing glow plug sleeve into bore</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Glow Plug Sleeve Installer</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Glow plug sleeve</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install glow plug sleeve into recess until it bottoms.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Clean glow plug sleeve after installation with a nylon brush and solvent. Make sure Liquid
                Gasket is cleaned out before it hardens.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
